{"tid":2008532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳沙中線最終調查報告  指紅磡站安全毋須拆除  中科潘焯鴻：對黨鐵禮頓最大獎品","createTime":"2020-05-09T06:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T07:36:38.000Z","uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac5085a557bd44bd344bd3bb67ecf90f206a00e","tid":2008532,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中綫前年被《蘋果》踢爆紅磡站剪短鋼筋及月台建築數據造假等問題，獨立調查委員會的最終報告至今年3月向特首提交。有報道引述消息指，最終報告仍認為紅磡站安全，毋須拆除，並猛烈批評港鐵公司、承建商禮頓及分判商中科。<br />\n<br />\n中科董事潘焯鴻說，委員會無權亦無能力判斷紅磡站結構是否安全，但報告判定該站結構安全，「係對港鐵同禮頓最大嘅獎品」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200504/4KAO2RT4HOEAGGO7RDMF7DPPY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200504%2F4KAO2RT4HOEAGGO7RDMF7DPPY4%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=98964ffb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200504%2F4KAO2RT4HOEAGGO7RDMF7DPPY4%2F&h=3af60889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200504/4KAO2RT4HOEAGGO7RDMF7DPPY4/</a>"},{"pid":"85f8734c44e202695848f69f78a6145f1e5191e8","tid":2008532,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa51ebd41b01c556b3f5c2bbab3f8f59f2a7d86","tid":2008532,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bc90844fc951f301ffe21298121cc129724521","tid":2008532,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"831隱瞞真相的報酬"},{"pid":"af2afc09a6f505b31bfbda33e7bde96f853df3c1","tid":2008532,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01bc90844fc951f301ffe21298121cc129724521","tid":2008532,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyT